Getting torrent errors on most of your uploads for June 7th, Cap. Say, the new Tantaros show is great! When you feed me, I feed 4 others. I give them the 'casts nightly. You *are* appreciated, my friend. If I could figure this out, I'd team with you!!
I looked at some tutorials on Y-Tube, but they did everything too fast. Some day! Been practicing w. Audacity, too. Not much of a geek here.
